OL,3,CShoplifter banned from every BP garage
OL,4,Cin the county where she lives
OL,6,FA persistent Southend shoplifter has
OL,7,Fbeen banned from every BP garage and
OL,8,Fstore across Essex for two years.
OL,10,FStacey Samuels, 35, has also been
OL,11,Fprohibited from entering the Co-op
OL,12,Fstore in Hamlet Court Road, Westcliff,
OL,13,Fduring that time.
OL,15,FSamuels admitted 39 counts of shop
OL,16,Ftheft totalling almost #1,600 of
OL,17,Fgoods, including meat, ready meals,
OL,18,Fboxes of chocolates and bottles of
OL,19,Fwine, between 28 January and 24 March
OL,20,F2024.
