OL,3,CShoplifter banned from every BP garage
OL,4,Cin the county where she lives
OL,6,FShe also admitted two attempted shop
OL,7,Fthefts, possession of cannabis and
OL,8,Fpossession of cocaine, when she
OL,9,Fappeared at Basildon magistrates court.
OL,11,FSamuels, of Prince Avenue, Westcliff,
OL,12,Ftargeted the BP garage in West Street,
OL,13,FWestcliff, as well as the Co-op in
OL,14,FHamlet Court Road, over a two-month
OL,15,Fperiod, the court heard.
OL,17,FSergeant Steve Wells, of Southend Town
OL,18,FCentre Team, said: "Samuels is a
OL,19,Fpersistent shoplifter but my team
OL,20,Fcaught up with her and she's had to
OL,21,Fface the consequences of her actions.
