OL,3,CShoplifter banned from every BP garage
OL,4,Cin the county where she lives
OL,6,F"I hope staff in the stores she
OL,7,Ftargeted feel safer now she's been
OL,8,Fbanned from entering them and in the
OL,9,Fknowledge that, if she breaches her
OL,10,Fcriminal behaviour order, she could be
OL,11,Fjailed.
OL,13,F"And I also hope Samuels takes the
OL,14,Fopportunity the court gave her to get
OL,15,Ftreatment for her addiction and, thus,
OL,16,Fremove the root cause of her offending
OL,17,Fbehaviour."
OL,19,FAs well as the two-year criminal
OL,20,Fbehaviour order, magistrates also
OL,21,Fimposed an 18-month community order.
